Author: bunchofbroccoli
Text: There's also Renfrew in Towson and Bethesda and the Body Image Therapy Center in Baltimore, Columbia, and DC. The Body Image Therapy Center offers partial hospitalization, which is an all-day program with an option to live in apartments nearby the center, if that is appealing to you.
